**************
The solution calculates \( D_e \) by first finding the zero-point energy \( E_{zp} \) using the given vibrational constants and then adding it to \( D_0 \). The computation yields \( D_e = 2.515120 \, \text{eV} \), which is rounded to four decimal places as \( 2.5151 \, \text{eV} \) based on the significant figures in the input data.

